%% Instantly Shareable Playtest — End-to-End Data Flow
%% Render with any Mermaid-compatible tool (VS Code extension, GitHub, etc.)

sequenceDiagram
    participant Creator as Game Creator
    participant Portal as xplaytest Portal<br/>(PlayTestFD)
    participant PlayTest as PlayTest Core
    participant PR as Partner Registry
    participant GSSV as Game Streaming<br/>Services (GSSV)
    participant Bayside as Play Xbox<br/>(Bayside)
    participant Tester as Playtester

    Note over Creator, Tester: === PLAYTEST CREATION ===

    Creator->>Portal: Create playtest (cloud streaming enabled)
    Portal->>PlayTest: POST /products/{id}/playtests
    PlayTest->>PR: POST /v1/offerings (create private offering)
    PR-->>PlayTest: offering ID, offering URL
    PlayTest-->>Portal: playtest created + streaming link
    Portal-->>Creator: Shareable streaming link

    Note over Creator, Tester: === AUDIENCE CONFIGURATION ===

    Creator->>Portal: Set audience DNA group
    Portal->>PlayTest: Update playtest audience
    PlayTest->>PR: PATCH /v1/offerings/{id} (update DNA group config)
    PR-->>PlayTest: OK

    Note over Creator, Tester: === BUILD UPLOAD & INGESTION ===

    Creator->>Portal: Upload new game build
    Portal->>PlayTest: Publish build to playtest
    PlayTest->>PlayTest: ServiceBus: XPackagePlaytestPublishWorkflow
    PlayTest->>GSSV: Ingest build into Game Streaming Services
    GSSV-->>PlayTest: Build ingested
    PlayTest->>PR: PUT /v1/offerings/{id}/titles (configure title with new build)
    PR-->>PlayTest: OK
    Note over GSSV: Build now streamable via private offering

    Note over Creator, Tester: === TESTER STREAMING ===

    Creator->>Tester: Share streaming link
    Tester->>Bayside: Click link
    Bayside->>Bayside: Authenticate user (login required first)
    Bayside->>GSSV: GET /offerings (check DNA group membership)
    GSSV-->>Bayside: Private offering details (if authorized)
    alt User is in DNA group
        Bayside->>Tester: Show playtest details + "Stream Now" button
        Tester->>Bayside: Click "Stream Now"
        Bayside->>GSSV: Start streaming session
        GSSV-->>Tester: Game stream
    else User NOT in DNA group
        Bayside->>Tester: Access denied (no details leaked)
    end

    Note over Creator, Tester: === PLAYTEST DELETION ===

    Creator->>Portal: Delete playtest
    Portal->>PlayTest: DELETE /products/{id}/playtests/{playtestId}
    PlayTest->>PR: DELETE /v1/offerings/{id}
    PR-->>PlayTest: Offering cleaned up
